- \(P(W \mid B_1) = \frac{2}{2} = 1\), \(P(B_1) = \frac{1}{2}\)  
- \(P(W \mid B_2) = \frac{0}{2} = 0\), \(P(B_2) = \frac{1}{4}\)  
- \(P(W \mid B_3) = \frac{2}{4} = 0.5\), \(P(B_3) = \frac{1}{8}\)  
- \(P(W \mid B_4) = \frac{3}{4} = 0.75\), \(P(B_4) = \frac{1}{8}\)  

