17% - 5.95% - 7.15% = 3.90%.

The percentage with low blood pressure is 19%, which includes both irregular and regular heartbeat cases. Therefore, the percentage with both regular heartbeat and low blood pressure is:
19% - 3.90% = 15.10%.

